<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 00:55:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>多头闯入中国股市，但外国人不敢进去</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/bulls-beat-path-china-stock-shop-foreigners-dare-not-go-2024-05-21/</link><description>受到中国最新措施和解决其陷入困境的经济最薄弱部分的承诺的鼓舞，国内投资者正在廉价股市中买入股票，而大多数外国投资者对此充满希望，但进展缓慢。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 23:11:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/bulls-beat-path-china-stock-shop-foreigners-dare-not-go-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>英国警方调查一名被控为中国从事间谍活动的男子不明原因死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-police-investigating-unexplained-death-man-charged-with-spying-china-2024-05-21/</link><description>英国警方正在调查一名本月早些时候被指控协助香港外国情报部门的男子不明原因死亡事件。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 19:09:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-police-investigating-unexplained-death-man-charged-with-spying-china-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>松下首席执行官表示，电动汽车普及速度放缓可能会推迟松下电动汽车电池的扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/slowing-ev-uptake-may-delay-panasonics-ev-battery-expansion-ceo-says-2024-05-21/</link><description>日本松下集团首席执行官表示，美国电动汽车使用放缓可能会促使特斯拉供应商松下推迟投资额外工厂，以提高其在北美的汽车电池产能。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 17:05:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/slowing-ev-uptake-may-delay-panasonics-ev-battery-expansion-ceo-says-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>尽管增长转向海外，香奈儿仍将在中国开设更多门店</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chanel-open-more-stores-china-even-growth-shifts-abroad-2024-05-21/</link><description>法国品牌香奈儿周二表示，尽管中国消费者在恢复旅行后将消费转向其他市场，但该公司仍计划在中国大陆投资开设更多门店。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 16:03:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chanel-open-more-stores-china-even-growth-shifts-abroad-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国化石揭示了羽毛恐龙皮肤的进化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/science/chinese-fossil-reveals-evolution-skin-feathered-dinosaurs-2024-05-21/</link><description>捐赠给中国一所大学的白垩纪恐龙鹦鹉嘴龙的新化石令人惊讶，这是一种狗大小的草食动物，长着鹦鹉般的喙——科学家在紫外线下观察后才发现它。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 15:06:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/science/chinese-fossil-reveals-evolution-skin-feathered-dinosaurs-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>土耳其和中国在部长访问期间讨论采矿、核能和可再生能源</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/turkey-china-discuss-mining-nuclear-renewable-energy-during-ministers-visit-2024-05-21/</link><description>土耳其能源部长周二表示，本周与中国当局和企业就采矿项目、核能和可再生能源举行了会谈，两国签署了一项能源转换初步协议。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 14:37:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/turkey-china-discuss-mining-nuclear-renewable-energy-during-ministers-visit-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>梵蒂冈枢机主教表示希望升级与中国的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/vatican-wants-upgrade-relations-with-china-top-cardinal-says-2024-05-21/</link><description>梵蒂冈枢机国务卿彼得罗·帕罗林周二表示，梵蒂冈希望在中国设立常设办事处，这将是与北京外交关系的重大升级。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 13:38:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/vatican-wants-upgrade-relations-with-china-top-cardinal-says-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>副总理表示，中国将控制房地产行业风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-will-control-property-sector-risk-says-vice-premier-2024-05-21/</link><description>国务院副总理何立峰周二表示，中国将控制房地产业、地方政府债务和小型地方金融机构等相互交织的风险。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 12:14:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-will-control-property-sector-risk-says-vice-premier-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国科技巨头大幅削减用于人工智能聊天机器人的语言模型的价格</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-tech-giants-slash-prices-language-models-used-power-ai-chatbots-2024-05-21/</link><description>随着中国云计算领域的价格战愈演愈烈，中国科技巨头阿里巴巴和百度周二大幅下调了用于生成人工智能产品的大语言模型（LLM）的价格。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 10:45:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-tech-giants-slash-prices-language-models-used-power-ai-chatbots-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国外交部长称台湾新总统“可耻”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-foreign-minister-calls-taiwans-new-president-disgraceful-2024-05-21/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅周二称台湾新上任的总统赖清德“可耻”，在他上任一天后加强了北京的言论。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 10:26:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-foreign-minister-calls-taiwans-new-president-disgraceful-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国京东计划通过可转换债券交易筹集 15 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-jdcom-aims-raise-15-bln-convertible-bond-deal-2024-05-21/</link><description>中国在线零售商京东周二向监管机构提交的文件显示，该公司将通过发行可转换债券筹集 15 亿美元资金。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 10:06:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-jdcom-aims-raise-15-bln-convertible-bond-deal-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：平静的市场徘徊在高点附近，金属回落</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-21/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 10:02:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>耶伦推动七国集团联合应对中国工业产能过剩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/yellen-says-us-europe-must-respond-jointly-chinas-industrial-overcapacity-2024-05-21/</link><description>美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦周二表示，美国和欧洲需要以“战略和统一的方式”应对中国的工业产能过剩，以保持大西洋两岸制造商的生存能力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 09:41:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/yellen-says-us-europe-must-respond-jointly-chinas-industrial-overcapacity-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>由于促销活动刺激了电动汽车需求，中国小鹏汽车季度交付量增加</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-forecasts-rise-quarterly-deliveries-2024-05-21/</link><description>小鹏汽车周二预测第二季度交付量将增加，因为降价有助于这家电动汽车制造商在竞争激烈的中国市场吸引更多买家，导致其在美国上市的股价上涨 8%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 09:38:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-forecasts-rise-quarterly-deliveries-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国制裁前美国议员和台湾支持者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-imposes-sanctions-ex-us-lawmaker-mike-gallagher-2024-05-21/</link><description>中国外交部周二表示，中国已禁止美国前议员迈克·加拉格尔入境，并采取其他措施回应他“干涉中国内政”的言行。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 09:08:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-imposes-sanctions-ex-us-lawmaker-mike-gallagher-2024-05-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>